d7331ac9af2168b6f3f4d73dae8b50edc8d539","tid":1596414,"uid":85051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:07:03.000Z","msg":"小弟之前開過關於連登重整旗鼓嘅建議Po<br />\n紅色為新增/修改項目<br />\n<br />\n1. Post自我分類，可以係前面加翻[行動Po] / [文宣Po] / [待FC] / [已FC] / [情報Po] / [國際線] / <span style=\"color: red;\">[突發]</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 需要巴絲打氣，可以開Po係感情台<br />\n(避免詳談夢境）<br />\n<br />\n3. 多分享抗爭一方嘅食店 / 店鋪嘅服務，舒緩身心，又可以俾大家有得唞一唞<br />\n<br />\n4. 多聽多唱肥媽首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個人會鬆啲<br />\n<br />\n5. 重推十點鐘光復時間<br />\n<br />\n6. 惜字如金，冷處理分化撚/失敗撚/五毛嘅言論，想鬧佢地可以開口鬧，唔需要係連登回應佢地<br />\n<br />\n7. 推Po直接打「721 811 831 新屋嶺」/<br />\n貼文宣圖 / <span style=\"color: red;\">行動日期時間地點</span>，唔打「推」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"517879510033f0405c62bd40aa0ce8caed3dbb3b","tid":1596414,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:14:47.000Z","msg":"狗樣"},{"pid":"4874eeb7ce40cbb533234d997f8316294dad29ad","tid":1596414,"uid":246446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:19:23.000Z","msg":"捉FA鬼單野係咪炒左車？"},{"pid":"107bbf6d626c17987e1a2df6ab82d1f0d98f714e","tid":1596414,"uid":250444,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:36:38.000Z","msg":"On9 , 假記者洗撚用甘柒大部機 ， 再者成日講 ， 保護好自己 ， 大把籃絲鬼撚鼠鼠用部電話影撚完你都唔會知 ， 又玩捉鬼 ？"},{"pid":"64d75fd82f5a314056862b5b6de6b8cbee9254fe","tid":1596414,"uid":41496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf2ba3a9196f71e72194ce1664f501bc6be7b5c9","tid":1596414,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:39:47.000Z","msg":"，"}]}